Im really excited to build out the Mooshimeter example to be able to read out both channels on the multimeter.

### Almost There

The Bluetooth Driver is about 60% done at this point. I still need to add security functionality (pairing, encryption, etc.), hardware functionality to be able to use the through-holes at the bottom, and the ability to update the firmware of the BlueGiga module itself over UART. Then Ill be polishing up a comprehensive test suite so that we can continuously integrate any new changes to the driver. Its a lot of work for one module, but totally worth it.

